{"type": "article", "id": 27851, "title": "香薰灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-07T06:51:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021105101F2tEdpGLyH863Us.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>来自韩国的 <a href=\"http://250.or.kr/\">250 Design</a> 工作室推出了一款既能提供照明又能为你的房间带来芬芳的香薰灯 Ro。椭球型的硅胶灯罩看上去很像是一个传统的灯笼，顶端是一块陶瓷的香薰托板。使用的时候，只要将精油滴在上面，香气就会通过灯光散发的热量扩散开来，可以说是一举两得。它还能根据你的喜好发出两种光，一个是象征日光的白光，另一个是象征月亮的黄光。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021105084lJizQDchIyoAP0W.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021105088Gf19BneIY6Switm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110509V4Rdm76iEKeanLlZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110509q1jYawJrkI5RgHmW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}